ary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Clarifying tool usage**\\n\\nI need to provide an answer without using any tools. I might mention session keys from spawn that are accepted and confirm that we have those. It's important to be honest that in run-mode, there are no codebase files available. I should note that the dashboard might not be visible due to being ephemeral or related to a different session namespace. Mentioning session keys could help clarify the situation.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] boss, they are **not in your codebase as files/folders**.\n\nThey were created as **runtime subagent runs**, not repo objects.\n\nHere’s exactly where they exist:\n\n- **Subagent 1 session key:** `agent:main:subagent:c02a2e32-99c7-429f-b08c-e8afc9f9a633`\n- **Subagent 2 session key:** `agent:main:subagent:e7f7633e-1bee-4f14-affe-ef66fcf1250e`\n\nWhat that means:\n- **codebase location:** nowhere as a folder/module/file unless I explicitly write one\n- **dashboard location:** not showing up for you as persistent dashboard agents because they were spawned as **`mode: \"run\"` one-shot jobs**, not thread-bound dashboard sessions\n- **workspace they would use if they touched files:** `/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace`\n\nSo the clean truth is:\n\n- you can’t find them in the repo because **they were never created in the repo**\n- you can’t find them in the dashboard as named persistent workers because **this Telegram path only let me create temporary run sessions**\n- they existed as **internal session records / run jobs**, not visible code artifacts\n\nThink:\n- **not files**\n- **not folders**\n- **not installed agents**\n- **just spawned runtime sessions**\n\nIf you want, I can fix the discoverability problem right now by creating:\n- `subagents/wolf-research-1.md`\n- `subagents/wolf-research-2.md`\n\nand put inside:\n- label\n- session key\n- purpose\n- status\n- created from which chat path\n\nThat way your kingly codebase stops hiding things like a raccoon with admin rights.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a05b6c3657906520169e7103960b88191b0d9010da9e052bf\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":30647,"output":433,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31080,"cost":{"input":0.0766175,"output":0.006495,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0831125}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776750644328}}
