\\nIf you want, boss, I can be stricter and tell you the three actual possibilities here:\\\\n\\\\n1. they were never really spawned and I described intended delegation,\\\\n2. they were spawned as temporary sessions and left no code folder,\\\\n3. they were ACP/subagent sessions outside the repo structure, so you wouldn’t “find them in codebase” at all.\\\\n\\\\nRight now, based on evidence, #2 or #1 looks more likely than “hidden folder in codebase.”\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nnow go and create 2 subgents the same way @wolf asked you and make sure they are visible in status and dashboard\"}],\"timestamp\":1776750127517}}\n22:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"5dfd0539\",\"parentId\":\"f4c25df2\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-21T05:42:15.706Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_0a05b6c3657906520169e70e308958819184e4af3e24795523\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp5w4z8z7B0cP9HqjH3hTtF449RGqZ-YqBmVsc1jRVc4rQ70O1yWBlAC6MO6wUsHa2LgQx1_1As-n4bas_fZkQq_T23qsQmWQv1W5YDY0a3tDxpAq5g3AwJcwS_09a9NBorj8fDU7h2L6Pd4X_0km7Z6U5Q2tjnisEeUl8w8LXrwtRLJimrUy1mQPZjc9Ai_NC3Wef3EOahHPtJfteRGTj9kv5Ymf3vhAXe5v4usUXjavBwCqa0T7BzALWFGWmwjE9ur98kCrJZQuyG4HW-M5Qnpvo-RHjuEHm12Te9vKwWJ-v0qaqV2VKZCnNoovXcraj_XI3nkou36MptNK3M1koW9WNfY-_x2iqn_mk1nusDgxxGrLS1XExJZcWZHYkLbnbdJ-Rs-ewwW2IhsFqrpBk8xKXWEEm8BIvvY5CYgMDGm9YW8blEFKE8zHqyDkE7t097bvyafnxuYQmtWkpdt2fcOTrKh3cDm4eH1fzS7sz_X7w-ShEm1chcnLYSCKSDQ7NWMPcaJuznfp95tVe9A3RK9nQ6-Q0QZQs5RpPv632t7weXX0WjvNzMPzmvCs2OI3bW1U4NyIWJKh88EtWOOHX38tnwq-BOvznh_i1wfdbgxeW_zXW3NllBZTj7iwcjTHLqLIM0Z4YBOd1AikVQy6cvkP9dHJK2QlaitpQdUZqoE_Og8n-IA99M9mnAcGWzV5ep9GH55pxtyma8apkcE3vNOHpGqFGdMHbuFavm1iimZCC8FcAYRAKgoaEDiR1aaPOQbabJQlUQKYfrTjPUySAv6UzfloMBWt_ikI-d-v7dygwQKGxJSXijh_0j4J15PA_e9YNLRtahbUbZ8nGVvgJPI5pLXSjcQhuahKYNhT_8vCtL47fDBIUwzJY3eMQGzysjrvUIflZB3eVQ0Y0NFXhv9KG_Pqxrn8OVWUFUfQTVRcxOKS3tYg9PwxhOAVAmYVwlAmkNGqZ_WwATcueRn_7L41JVVW3IXSOEr841C5MAVJWh